    PowerSDK
    Contains all the methods and the callbacks of mount and link 
     
 1，Initialize the connection of SDK
 execute startConnectSDK PowerSDK.startConnectSDK(com.powervision.powersdk.factory.base.BaseConnectIpAndPort) method
 
 2， Register the callback of SDK connection,otherwise,ConnectListener or ConnectListener.SimpleConnectListener (A simplified ConnectListener) ，
 don't need to implement all of the callback methods.callback methods called ConnectListener) would not be executed.
